t;https://news.tvb.com/tc/finance/687f111554d16ed89e10dd5a?utm_source=newsappshare&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有證券業人士認為大市短期有調整風險。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;紅蟻資本投資總監李澤銘稱︰「港股短期仍然有少少催化推升，但不是一些很大的利好消息。估計對於大盤的變動幅度不會很大。但個別板塊應該會輪流炒作。大市來說仍然有風險要特別注意，因為越接近八月一日。美國新關稅生效時候，其實市場風險會逐步累積。可能無論美股也好、港股也好。面對比較大的回調風險。」&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31988199&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1149402330687fbe2c7ddfe8_62789937"/><published>2025-07-22T16:19:17+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>37c9dbd8edb4e5f1ce323722a24a4763</id><title>單天保至尊</title><updated>2025-07-22T21:01:35+08:00</updated><author><name>uturn2</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-22T21:01:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573323475"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573323475"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F15113550-%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2582%25a1%25e5%25b8%2582%25e5%25a5%25bd-%25e7%259d%2587%25e6%25b7%25a1%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e9%259b%25a3&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=7b5ded4f3526bdc0bfb1a163b8c86b7f&amp;amp;fid=57" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.bastillepost.com/hon ... 5113550-香港股市好-睇淡經濟難&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31988416&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1149402330687fbe2c7ddfe8_62789937"/><published>2025-07-22T21:01:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c96c558e234e2e70e9bc311c4740dcb7</id><title>領展王國龍流馬尿啲戲真係好屎😆</title><updated>2025-07-22T21:04:35+08:00</upda